
# REBECA

> Risk Based Corrective Actions (RBCA)

Opensource tool to complete all calculations required for Tiers 1 and 2 by the ASTM-RBCA planning process, as defined in ASTM E-2081-00 Standard Guide for Risk-Based Corrective Action (ASTM, 2004) and ASTM E-1739-95 Standard Guide for Risk-Based Corrective Action Applied at Petroleum Release Sites (ASTM, 2002), and consistent with current U.S. EPA guidelines for human health risk assessment (U.S. EPA, 1989a, 1996).



